## cache_httpfs

Delegate Path V's block cache / parallel range IO / eviction to `cache_httpfs`
(community, "drop-in replacement for httpfs"). It only helps VFS reads — unlocked
*by* Path V, not a substitute for the shim. Our shim keeps only pgen-specific
offset-index range planning. Load it in the milestone-3 spike or the cached case is
under-measured.
